{"tid":203400,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透撚] FX - Fargo Season 3 劇情討論區","createTime":"2017-04-16T09:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T10:23:04.000Z","uid":54957,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43f8dee804be641e2e3725b36f5f7a4c6ca9611c","tid":203400,"uid":54957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37dL3yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37dL3yT.jpg&h=01ad5316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMetacritic: <a href=\"http://www.metacritic.com/tv/fargo/season-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metacritic.com%2Ftv%2Ffargo%2Fseason-3&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e03f44fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metacritic.com/tv/fargo/season-3</a><br />\n<br />\nR.T.: <a href=\"https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/fargo/s03/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rottentomatoes.com%2Ftv%2Ffargo%2Fs03%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=83faf5d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/fargo/s03/</a><br />\n<br />\nIndiewire: remains a Masterful Midwestern Drama　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/fargo-review-season-3-ewan-mcgregor-1201799639/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2017%2F04%2Ffargo-review-season-3-ewan-mcgregor-1201799639%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ac2cfdb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/fargo-review-season-3-ewan-mcgregor-1201799639/</a><br />\n<br />\n4月19就有得睇啦 今季total有10集<br />\n<br />\n線上看: <a href=\"http://vmus.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmus.co%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a3c617d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://vmus.co/</a>"},{"pid":"4db2124bfa7f9b1a01d877aab4c9c1014ec3ba0d","tid":203400,"uid":23977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd91986e79095c91157554b6ea5f3e316351335","tid":203400,"uid":8150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"留名睇carrie coon"},{"pid":"5668873cd4e815d3063dc6a526a79f19fa5f5123","tid":203400,"uid":54957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"4月19先有得睇，咁我就簡單推一推先<br />\n<br />\n哩幾年有一大堆改編電影嘅電視劇出現，唔理佢哋有幾多掛羊頭賣狗肉或者借電影嘅名氣來吸引觀眾，想拍到有返電影嘅水準或者嗰種味道出來嘅真係唔多，始終翻拍得嘅電影都珠玉在前，唔俾fans屌已經當你改編成功<br />\n<br />\n咁Fargo作為高安兄弟嘅代表作，竟然有人走去改編，一喺就藝高人膽大、一喺就賣狗肉，當年見FX出品，就當然狗衝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗著當懷舊吓都好，點知睇睇吓發覺套嘢同電影一樣咁撚神，仲要一季神過一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單資料：<br />\n未睇過電影都睇得套劇，不過你最好睇吓套電影，因為真係好撚好睇<br />\n<br />\n未睇過頭兩季都可以直接睇第三季，因為唔影響觀影，不過頭一二季無睇過就真係死咗佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鐘意睇黑色/幽默/存在主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /電影感/主角心理變化、成長/疏離....嘅你，快啲一齊睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d95c9babd093706f36b4f2d3343af79c17270","tid":203400,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0h81d03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0h81d03.jpg&h=ac261d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇緊S01E04"},{"pid":"ab87ebc6d6f66647aa5cea182b2bc3ceb5fb448e","tid":203400,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"大家好 我是來留名的"},{"pid":"3344742df262ef0108cef2ea1ee329e218f2c651","tid":203400,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c